The deeper pattern is something you’ve touched on before:

Text, audio, video, diagrams, simulations, and conversations are all different projections of the same underlying meaning structure.

The next generation of AI systems will likely treat “answering” as creating a reusable meaning object first, then rendering it into whatever medium best transfers understanding to the human on the other end. For learning-heavy topics like CPG, that medium is often video.